# Quality Reports Directory

This directory contains generated code quality reports. All contents are gitignored.

## Generate Reports

```bash
bun run report:all          # Generate all reports
bun run report:coverage     # Test coverage only
bun run quality:arch:report # Architecture HTML report
bun run quality:arch:viz    # Dependency graph SVG
bun run quality:eslint:report # ESLint JSON report
```

## Report Structure

```
reports/
├── coverage/               # Vitest coverage (HTML)
│   └── index.html
├── dependency-report.html  # Architecture violations
├── dependency-graph.svg    # Module dependency visualization
└── eslint-report.json      # ESLint issues (JSON)
```

## Viewing Reports

- **Coverage**: `open reports/coverage/index.html`
- **Architecture**: `open reports/dependency-report.html`
- **Dependency Graph**: `open reports/dependency-graph.svg`
